   \n\nA. I have got
\n\nB. my M.Sc. degree
\n\nC. in 1988.
\n\nD. No error."/>

        <View
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="2dp"
            android:layout_margin="8dp"
            android:background="#FFFFFF" />

        <TextView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="match_parent"
            android:textColor="#FFFFFF"
            android:text="\n\nQuestion 9:
